@startuml
title B8 Slice 3 - Version-Aware Retrieval

actor Agent
participant "Issue Retrieval Service" as IRS
database "Issue Protocol Artifacts" as IPA
database "Issue Merge Candidates" as IMC
database "Knowledge Document Versions" as KDV
database "Knowledge Chunks/Documents" as KD

Agent -> IRS : handleProtocolMessage(...)
IRS -> IPA : resolve diff/workspace artifact context
IRS -> IMC : fallback merge candidate context
IRS -> KD : query hybrid candidates
IRS -> KDV : load candidate version rows
IRS -> IRS : temporal rerank\nexact_commit / same_branch / stale / foreign
IRS --> Agent : brief + quality metrics

note right of IRS
Temporal scoring stays additive.
Hybrid retrieval remains the base signal.
end note
@enduml
